name: Stephine Parker
description: I was raised in a christian home with good morales and values. I’m family oriented and believe in stepping up to be the man for my family that I need to be. I treat others the way I want to be treated. I’m very big on respect and think respect is earned and not just given. I’m a firm believer in God and think life should be structured by putting him first, then family, then church. I’m a hardworker and everything I have I’ve worked for. I don’t claim to be perfect and have make a lot of mistakes in my life
